'''''"New Cutting Edge"''''' is a name of extended versions of '''''Cutting Edge''''' - [[English language|English]] multi-level books used for [[English language|English]] courses from the '''''Starter''''' to '''''Advanced''''' level that first published by [[Pearson Longman]] in 2005. The [[author]]s of the books are Peter Moor, Sarah Cunningham and sometimes added Jane Comyns Carr. 

